
                Commands available from the Alias Menu

Char    Meaning
----    -------

  ?     help on a specific key, or this summary of commands

  a     add return address of current message to alias database

  d     delete an alias from alias database

  e	check for an alias with full expanded addresses

  m     make new user alias, adding to alias database

  <return>
        return from the alias menu

  p     check for a person in the alias database

  s     check for aliases in the system alias database

  u     check for aliases in the user alias database
